ARTICLE.TITLE: Missing woman found
ARTICLE.TEXT:
UPDATE:

Spruiell has been found.

-----------------------------------------

Panama City Police need your help finding a woman they say is a missing endangered person.

Police say Jessie Spruiell, 20, was last seen Monday afternoon.

She is described as white with blond hair, fair skin, and green-blue eyes. Police say she has a tattoo of an octopus on her left forearm.

If you have any information on Spruiell's whereabouts, contact Panama City Police at 850-872-3100, or report your tips anonymously via the Panama City PD Tip411 app.
